                        <interp inst="t18510616-name-677" type="given" value="ALFRED"></interp>ALFRED SPICE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, V</hi> 47). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at the Quarter Sessions at Newington (<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted, Oct.</hi>, 1850, <hi rend="italic">confined three months, and whipped</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
